divs: sighting detailsi did not notice the objects when taking the photos of cheyenne mountain. the photos were taken by myself from the deck on the back of the lodge at cheyenne mountain resort where my family & i were on spring break vacation. i was on the deck with my daughter taking some pictures. i did not notice the objects when i was there or when i took the photos. after returning home i downloaded all my photos to my computer & kind of looked over them quickly. last night (7\24\12)i opened my doc file & started looking @ photos from colorado & came across the 2 photos with the strange lights. what do you think it is? my first thought upon see the lights was ufo.
